msgctxt "1392_Maya"
msgid "It looks like I've been requested."
msgstr "Parece que me han solicitado."

msgctxt "1404_Maya"
msgid "Please enjoy yourself."
msgstr "Por favor, diviértase."

msgctxt "1416_Maya"
msgid "Bye for now."
msgstr "Hasta luego."

msgctxt "1428_Maya"
msgid "Hello. I'm Maya."
msgstr "Hola. Soy Maya."

msgctxt "1440_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm Kazuma Kiryu. Nice to meet you."
msgstr "Soy Kazuma Kiryu. Encantado de conocerte."

msgctxt "1452_Maya"
msgid "Hi, Kiryu-san. It's nice to meet you too. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hola Kiryu-san. El gusto es todo mío.\n"\n"<Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1464_Kiryu"
msgid "Maya's a cute name. Is it your working name?"
msgstr "Maya es un nombre lindo, ¿lo usas para el trabajo?"

msgctxt "1476_Maya"
msgid "No, it's my real name. But most people call me Mayamori."
msgstr "No, es mi verdadero nombre. Pero mucha gente me dice Mayamori."

msgctxt "1488_Kiryu"
msgid "Can I call you that, too?"
msgstr "¿Puedo llamarte así también?"

msgctxt "1500_Maya"
msgid "Haha! Sure!"
msgstr "¡Ja, ja! ¡Claro que sí!"

msgctxt "1512_Maya"
msgid "What do people call you?"
msgstr "¿Y como te dicen a usted?"

msgctxt "1524_Kiryu"
msgid "Me? Well..."
msgstr "¿A mí? Bueno..."

msgctxt "1536_Kiryu"
msgid "Kiryu-san, mostly."
msgstr "Mayormente... Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "1548_Maya"
msgid "How original! Maybe I can think up an interesting nickname for you."
msgstr "¡Qué original! Tal vez pueda crear un apodo interesante para ti."

msgctxt "1560_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh, I'll pass. Thanks."
msgstr "Eh... Muchas gracias, pero paso."

msgctxt "1572_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that what they say when you get a request?"
msgstr "¿Eso es lo que dicen cuando te solicitan?"

msgctxt "1584_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. Maybe the waiters say, \"Request for Mayamori\"!"
msgstr "Je, je. Quizás los camareros dicen \"¡Pido a Mayamori!\""

msgctxt "1596_Maya"
msgid "You'll just have to request me to find out! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Pues tendrás que solicitarme para que lo averigües! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1608_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Maybe I'll do that."
msgstr "Je. Tal vez lo haga."

msgctxt "1620_Maya"
msgid "I'll be waiting!"
msgstr "¡Lo estaré esperando!"

msgctxt "1632_Kiryu"
msgid "What's your full name?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es tu nombre completo?"

msgctxt "1644_Maya"
msgid "Huh? I told you. Maya Mori."
msgstr "¿Eh? Si ya te lo dije: Maya Mori."

msgctxt "1656_Kiryu"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "1668_Maya"
msgid "Maya is my first name and Mori is my last name. Maya Mori."
msgstr "Maya is my first name and Mori is my last name. Maya Mori."

msgctxt "1680_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh! I thought it was a nickname."
msgstr "Oh! I thought it was a nickname."

msgctxt "1692_Maya"
msgid "Lots of people say that. Even people I've known for a long time have asked me:"
msgstr "Muchísima gente me lo dice. Incluso conocidos desde hace años me han preguntado:"

msgctxt "1704_Maya"
msgid "\"What's your real name, Mayamori-chan?\""
msgstr "\"What's your real name, Mayamori-chan?\""

msgctxt "1716_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. It's a good name. Easy to remember."
msgstr "Heh. It's a good name. Easy to remember."

msgctxt "1728_Maya"
msgid "Then you won't have any trouble requesting me, will you?"
msgstr "Then you won't have any trouble requesting me, will you?"

msgctxt "1740_Maya"
msgid "You're very fashion-conscious, aren't you?"
msgstr "Eres fanático de la moda, ¿no?"

msgctxt "1752_Kiryu"
msgid "You think so?"
msgstr "¿De verdad lo cree?"

msgctxt "1764_Maya"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "1776_Maya"
msgid "Everybody should pay more attention to fashion once they're adults. As long as they have the money for it, of course."
msgstr "Todo el mundo debería prestar más atención a la moda cuando sean adultos. Siempre y cuando tengan dinero para costearlo, claro está."

msgctxt "1788_Kiryu"
msgid "You keep an eye on that kind of thing, huh?"
msgstr "Estás atenta en ese tipo de cosas, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "1800_Maya"
msgid "Yep. I'm kind of picky when it comes to clothes."
msgstr "Sip. Soy exigente cuando se trata de la ropa."

msgctxt "1812_Kiryu"
msgid "I like to dress casual when I'm not working. In fact, this is the only suit I have."
msgstr "Me gusta vestirme casual cuando no estoy trabajando. De hecho, este es el único traje que tengo disponible."

msgctxt "1824_Maya"
msgid "Oh? Well, it's a nice one."
msgstr "¿Oh? Bueno, es una bonita."

msgctxt "1836_Maya"
msgid "A person's clothes can really affect the impression they give. And you make a great first impression."
msgstr "La ropa de una persona puede influir mucho en la impresión que da. Y tu guapo, das una muy buena impresión."

msgctxt "1848_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, thanks. You look nice in that dress, too."
msgstr "Gracias. Te ves bien en ese vestido."

msgctxt "1860_Maya"
msgid "Really? Thank you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Really? Thank you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1872_Kiryu"
msgid "It takes more than money to be well-dressed. You have to have taste, too."
msgstr "Se necesita más que dinero para estar bien vestido. También hay que tener buen gusto."

msgctxt "1884_Maya"
msgid "Right! You can look great wearing old clothes, as long as they're the right old clothes."
msgstr "Sí. Puedes estar estupendo con ropa vieja, siempre que sea la ropa vieja adecuada."

msgctxt "1896_Kiryu"
msgid "I've got to pick out clothes for the kids I look after, so I guess I pay more attention to that kind of thing than most people."
msgstr "Tengo que elegir ropa para los niños que cuido, así que supongo que pongo más atención a ese tipo de cosas que la mayoría de la gente."

msgctxt "1908_Maya"
msgid "Wow. You're a trendsetter, then!"
msgstr "Wow. You're a trendsetter, then!"

msgctxt "1920_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, sure."
msgstr "Je, como tú digas."

msgctxt "1932_Kiryu"
msgid "You shouldn't judge a man by his clothes. Some people won't look good no matter what they wear."
msgstr "No deberías juzgar a un hombre por como va vestido. A veces, algunas personas no se verán bien, sin importar que lleven puesto."

msgctxt "1944_Maya"
msgid "Well, you have to wear clothes that match your body type."
msgstr "Bueno, tienes que llevar ropa que combine con tu tipo de cuerpo."

msgctxt "1956_Maya"
msgid "You're nice and muscular, so you'd look great in foreign brand-name clothes."
msgstr "Eres atractivo y musculoso. Te verías bien con ropa  de marca extranjera."

msgctxt "1968_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, clothing can be hard to move in. I often end up taking my shirt off."
msgstr "Bueno, la ropa puede ser difícil de ponerse. A menudo me termino quitando la camisa."

msgctxt "1980_Maya"
msgid "Really!? That's kind of a waste."
msgstr "¿¡En serio!? Qué manera de desperdiciarlo."

msgctxt "1992_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm more confident in how I look without clothes, actually.\\r\n"\n"Maybe I'll show you sometime."
msgstr "Me siento más seguro de como me veo sin ropa. De hecho,\\r tal vez te lo muestre en algún momento."

msgctxt "2004_Maya"
msgid "Oh! Uh, I'll think about it!"
msgstr "¡Oh!, ah, ¡lo pensaré!"

msgctxt "2016_Maya"
msgid "Welcome back. It's nice to see you again! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Welcome back. It's nice to see you again! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2028_Kiryu"
msgid "You too."
msgstr "You too."

msgctxt "2040_Maya"
msgid "So, did you find a girl you like?"
msgstr "So, did you find a girl you like?"

msgctxt "2052_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. I'm looking at her right now."
msgstr "Yeah. I'm looking at her right now."

msgctxt "2064_Maya"
msgid "Hahaha! You're going to make me blush!"
msgstr "Hahaha! You're going to make me blush!"

msgctxt "2076_Maya"
msgid "If you like me so much, why don't you request me next time?"
msgstr "If you like me so much, why don't you request me next time?"

msgctxt "2088_Kiryu"
msgid "All right. I'll do that."
msgstr "All right. I'll do that."

msgctxt "2100_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've\\r\n"\n"entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."
msgstr "El diálogo terminará después de una ronda\\r\n"\n"cuando entre al club más de una vez. Contacte a un programador si ve este mensaje."

msgctxt "2112_Maya"
msgid "Kiryu-san... You didn't request me today..."
msgstr "Kiryu-san... You didn't request me today..."

msgctxt "2124_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, right. I didn't mean anything by it. I just wanted a little change of pace."
msgstr "Oh, right. I didn't mean anything by it. I just wanted a little change of pace."

msgctxt "2136_Maya"
msgid "I've been staying here because you request me, but maybe I'll quit after all."
msgstr "I've been staying here because you request me, but maybe I'll quit after all."

msgctxt "2148_Kiryu"
msgid "Wait a minute. Don't do anything hasty. I'll request you next time. I promise."
msgstr "Wait a minute. Don't do anything hasty. I'll request you next time. I promise."

msgctxt "2160_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. Cross your heart? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hehe. Cross your heart? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2172_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've\\r\n"\n"entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."
msgstr "El diálogo terminará después de una ronda\\r\n"\n"cuando entre al club más de una vez. Contacte a un programador si ve este mensaje."

