msgctxt "2400_Maya"
msgid "I'm Maya. Nice to meet you."
msgstr "Soy Maya. Encantada de conocerte."

msgctxt "2412_Tanimura"
msgid "I'm Tanimura."
msgstr "Yo soy Tanimura."

msgctxt "2424_Maya"
msgid "What do you do for a living?"
msgstr "¿A qué te dedicas?"

msgctxt "2436_Tanimura"
msgid "You girls like asking that question, don't you? I'm a cop."
msgstr "A las chicas les gusta hacer esa pregunta, ¿no? Soy policía."

msgctxt "2448_Maya"
msgid "You are!?"
msgstr "¡¿En serio?!"

msgctxt "2460_Tanimura"
msgid "It's not that surprising, is it? You must get other cops coming here to drink once in a while."
msgstr "No es para tanto, ¿cierto? Seguro que otros policías vienen por aquí a beber de vez en cuando."

msgctxt "2472_Maya"
msgid "Actually, I get stopped by the police quite often. I even got stopped on my way here today. So yes, I do see a lot of cops."
msgstr "En realidad, la policía me suele detener con frecuencia. Incluso hoy me detuvieron cuando venía. Así que sí, veo un montón de policías."

msgctxt "2484_Tanimura"
msgid "Heh. Small world."
msgstr "Je, qué pequeño es el mundo."

msgctxt "2496_Maya"
msgid "Did you always want to be a policeman?"
msgstr "¿Siempre quisiste ser policía?"

msgctxt "2508_Tanimura"
msgid "You could say that. My father was a cop, too."
msgstr "Se podría decir que sí. Mi padre también fue policía."

msgctxt "2520_Maya"
msgid "Wow, that's great! I work as a fashion model when I'm not here."
msgstr "¡Guau, eso es genial! Yo trabajo de modelo cuando no estoy en el club."

msgctxt "2532_Tanimura"
msgid "That sounds pretty impressive."
msgstr "Oh, eso suena asombroso."

msgctxt "2544_Maya"
msgid "I've wanted to be a model for so long, it's like a dream come true."
msgstr "He querido ser modelo durante mucho tiempo, es como un sueño hecho realidad."

msgctxt "2556_Tanimura"
msgid "Do you have a goal as a model? Like appearing in a fashion show overseas or something?"
msgstr "¿Tienes algún propósito como modelo? Algo así como..., ¿ir a un desfile de moda en el extranjero?"

msgctxt "2568_Maya"
msgid "No, I'm just happy to be able to do what I love."
msgstr "Nah, ya soy feliz de poder hacer lo que me gusta."

msgctxt "2580_Tanimura"
msgid "You're pretty modest, aren't you?"
msgstr "Je, je. Parece que eres muy modesta."

msgctxt "2592_Maya"
msgid "Were you working again today? You must be tired."
msgstr "Were you working again today? You must be tired."

msgctxt "2604_Tanimura"
msgid "Hmm? Oh, yeah. You could say I'm still on the job, actually."
msgstr "Hmm? Oh, yeah. You could say I'm still on the job, actually."

msgctxt "2616_Maya"
msgid "Haha! Are you sure it's okay for you to be in a place like this, then?"
msgstr "Haha! Are you sure it's okay for you to be in a place like this, then?"

msgctxt "2628_Tanimura"
msgid "We'll call it fieldwork. I have to know the conditions on the ground before I can move in and make an arrest, right?"
msgstr "We'll call it fieldwork. I have to know the conditions on the ground before I can move in and make an arrest, right?"

msgctxt "2640_Maya"
msgid "Hmm? Someone here is breaking the law?"
msgstr "Hmm? Someone here is breaking the law?"

msgctxt "2652_Tanimura"
msgid "Could be. I wouldn't be doing my job if I didn't give this place a thorough look."
